data.title: Varun Dhawan is back with his new movie, Baby John, set to release on December 25! After multiple delays, the makers finally revealed the...
data.meta_description:
7 likes, 0 comments - filmishorts on June 27, 2024: "Varun Dhawan is back with his new movie, Baby John, set to release on December 25! After multiple delays, the makers finally revealed the release date along with a new poster.

The film, directed by A. Kaleeswaran and produced by Murad K hetani, Priya Atlee, and Jyoti Deshpande, promises stunning visual effects and action sequences. 

Baby John also features Keerthy Suresh, Wamiqa Gabbi, Jackie Shroff, and Rajpal Yadav. Excitement is building as it will clash with Aamir Khan's Sitaare Zameen Par on Christmas Day. Get ready for an epic holiday showdown!
.
.
